comments: Anunoby (TOR) and Jokic (DEN) mutually engage and disengage in the post.
Jokic (DEN) and Trent Jr. (TOR) briefly engage in marginal contact prior to separating.
Jokic (DEN) slightly extends his arm and he makes marginal contact to Siakam's (TOR) side that does not affect his agility to defend.
Barnes (TOR) maintains a legal vertical position during Jokic's (DEN) driving shot attempt.
Hyland (DEN) makes contact to VanVleet's (TOR) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Anunoby (TOR) makes contact with the ball as Barton (DEN) is gathering the ball, the contact does not affect Barton's ability to gather the ball.
Barnes (TOR) briefly places his arm across Barton's (DEN) front as he comes to a stop but Barnes immediately removes his arm. Barton moves through the marginal contact.
Siakam (TOR) commits take foul on Jokic (DEN).
Barton (DEN) makes marginal contact with Siakam's (TOR) arm that does not affect his SQBR.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Anunoby (TOR) slightly extends his arm into Green's (DEN) front during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with the ball during Anunoby's (TOR) shot attempt near the rim.
